{
  "stem": "12491.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And eventually, we got the a response from the Czechoslovakian underground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Which, as I mentioned before, that if we can hold them up for six hours, they will be able to help.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was how much time they need to mobilize.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So now you're in the booth with the whole group of underground, holding your weapons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How many weapons in all did you end up with?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had six rifles, a machine gun, and several side arms, revolvers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was given the revolver because I got the stupid job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is something which has to be started again, with a different end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the people who were frozen in the train arrived, with them arrived another prisoner what was known as [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] which is professional criminal, who was a German, not a Jew, who was a kapo in the camp from which these Jews came.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was at Camp Schindler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he also was revived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was always OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He became very strong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he tried to carry his weight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we were in charge.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He couldn't carry his weight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was no longer a kapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we interviewed-- not we, I say we, I mean some of the 28, not I-- and found out how many people he killed in the camp he came from.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What they used to do is, they used to get-- a kapo used to get an assignment of, let's say, so many breads.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the fewer breads you give out, the more he had for himself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you killed three people today, you got three portions of bread extra.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was his.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is why they killed people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Eventually I got the responsibility of guarding him till some authority would arrive and decide what to do with him.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
